1
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:49,972
DESTINED WITH YOU

2
00:00:52,683 --> 00:00:54,601
EPISODE 3

3
00:01:20,335 --> 00:01:22,629
NA-YEON

4
00:01:29,803 --> 00:01:30,804
Halo?

5
00:03:43,478 --> 00:03:44,980
Dia menunggu lama.

6
00:03:45,939 --> 00:03:47,691
Kutunggu dia bangun sendiri.

7
00:03:47,774 --> 00:03:48,775
Baik.

8
00:04:03,206 --> 00:04:04,541
Aku tak mau bangun.

9
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:07,377
Aku mati 30 menit lalu.

10
00:04:11,715 --> 00:04:13,592
Orang tercintamu sudah tiada.

11
00:04:13,675 --> 00:04:15,051
Kenapa kau tak cemas?

12
00:04:23,435 --> 00:04:24,435
Aduh.

13
00:04:25,061 --> 00:04:26,313
Sudah terlambat.

14
00:04:26,897 --> 00:04:28,899
Kubilang cepat. Kau sengaja, 'kan?

15
00:04:29,608 --> 00:04:30,942
Kau tak cinta aku lagi.

16
00:04:31,651 --> 00:04:32,819
Aku kecelakaan.

17
00:04:32,903 --> 00:04:35,989
Aku kirim mobilnya ke bengkel
dan naik taksi ke sini.

18
00:04:36,865 --> 00:04:37,949
Jadi, aku telat.

19
00:04:38,033 --> 00:04:39,493
Kenapa kau ke sini?

20
00:04:39,576 --> 00:04:40,827
Pergi ke rumah sakit.

21
00:04:40,911 --> 00:04:42,579
Kau ingin bertemu denganku.

22
00:04:42,662 --> 00:04:43,705
Harus kukabulkan.

23
00:04:44,289 --> 00:04:45,624
Kau gila?

24
00:04:45,707 --> 00:04:47,042
Ayo ke rumah sakit.

25
00:04:47,751 --> 00:04:49,085
Ini bukan apa-apa.

26
00:04:50,295 --> 00:04:51,755
Kenapa bukan apa-apa?

27
00:04:52,255 --> 00:04:54,925
Itu kecelakaan. Efeknya akan terasa nanti.

28
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:59,429
Kau akan bilang punggungmu sakit
dan enggan bulan madu yang jauh.

29
00:04:59,513 --> 00:05:00,722
Aku benci itu.

30
00:05:04,601 --> 00:05:05,769
Itu tak mungkin.

31
00:05:13,151 --> 00:05:14,319
Na-yeon.

32
00:05:19,282 --> 00:05:20,909
Aku tahu ada sesuatu

33
00:05:20,992 --> 00:05:24,120
saat kau memilih berhenti
dan pindah ke Onju sendiri.

34
00:05:24,704 --> 00:05:27,415
Ayah gembira.
Dia bilang kau ingin membantunya.

35
00:05:27,499 --> 00:05:29,000
Namun, dia salah, 'kan?

36
00:05:31,169 --> 00:05:32,879
Temanku akan menikah.

37
00:05:32,963 --> 00:05:34,714
Aku diminta menangkap buket.

38
00:05:35,257 --> 00:05:36,550
Maka itu aku minum.

39
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:40,762
Lalu, kami membahas siapa
yang menangkap buketku.

40
00:05:43,348 --> 00:05:44,808
Kenapa harus hari ini?

41
00:05:51,731 --> 00:05:53,024
Aku mau tanya.

42
00:05:54,484 --> 00:05:55,652
Apa kita putus?

43
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,321
Lalu, apa ini?

44
00:05:59,030 --> 00:06:00,657
Kenapa butuh waktu? Untuk apa?

45
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,534
Ada yang harus kuselesaikan.

46
00:06:02,617 --> 00:06:04,244
Kita selesaikan bersama.

47
00:06:04,327 --> 00:06:06,162
Harus kuselesaikan sendiri.

48
00:06:10,667 --> 00:06:12,043
Bisa tunggu sebentar?

49
00:06:20,218 --> 00:06:22,971
<i>"Saat mawar mulai mekar di dalam susu,</i>

50
00:06:26,308 --> 00:06:29,853
<i>bakar halaman ini
dan campurkan dengan semua bahan."</i>

51
00:06:41,948 --> 00:06:44,242
<i>"Saat mawar mekar sepenuhnya,</i>

52
00:06:44,326 --> 00:06:45,994
<i>saringlah dengan kain."</i>

53
00:06:47,203 --> 00:06:49,289
<i>"Saat airnya jernih…</i>

54
00:06:53,418 --> 00:06:54,878
<i>itu ramuan cinta."</i>

55
00:07:01,259 --> 00:07:05,305
<i>"Buat target cintamu meminumnya."</i>

56
00:07:17,442 --> 00:07:18,818
KOTA ONJU

57
00:07:19,861 --> 00:07:20,946
Su-yeong.

58
00:07:21,029 --> 00:07:22,864
- Mari arahkan yang di lobi.
- Ya.

59
00:07:33,416 --> 00:07:35,168
RAPAT UMUM ONJEONG-DONG

60
00:07:41,174 --> 00:07:42,717
PENASIHAT KWON JAE-GYEONG

61
00:08:14,457 --> 00:08:15,457
Semoga ampuh.

62
00:08:36,271 --> 00:08:37,939
Selamat pagi.

63
00:08:38,523 --> 00:08:41,109
Belakangan ini sibuk, 'kan? Terima kasih.

64
00:08:41,192 --> 00:08:42,777
Silakan duduk.

65
00:08:42,861 --> 00:08:43,861
Ya.

66
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,032
- Pak Park.
- Ya?

67
00:08:47,115 --> 00:08:49,826
Selamat atas masuknya putramu
ke universitas.

68
00:08:49,909 --> 00:08:50,952
Terima kasih.

69
00:08:51,036 --> 00:08:52,370
- Nanti traktir kami?
- Ya.

70
00:08:52,454 --> 00:08:54,456
- Akan kuingat.
- Terima kasih.

71
00:09:04,174 --> 00:09:05,174
Astaga.

72
00:09:08,762 --> 00:09:09,846
Ya, Pak Gong.

73
00:09:09,929 --> 00:09:11,347
<i>Kau membolos?</i>

74
00:09:12,057 --> 00:09:14,976
- Aku ada urusan.
<i>- Wali Kota mengamuk karenamu.</i>

75
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:16,061
Apa?

76
00:09:16,144 --> 00:09:17,520
<i>Cepat kembali.</i>

77
00:09:17,604 --> 00:09:18,604
Baik.

78
00:09:22,192 --> 00:09:24,444
Tugas utama Divisi Tata Kota,

79
00:09:24,527 --> 00:09:28,406
daftar periksa, dan analisis kasus.

80
00:09:28,990 --> 00:09:30,575
Siapa mau maju pertama?

81
00:09:30,658 --> 00:09:31,868
Diminum atau tidak?

82
00:09:35,371 --> 00:09:37,415
KOTA ONJU

83
00:09:41,628 --> 00:09:42,754
Cek Onjeong-dong.

84
00:09:42,837 --> 00:09:45,381
- Pot gantungnya hancur.
- Kenapa hancur?

85
00:09:45,965 --> 00:09:47,092
Mana aku tahu?

86
00:09:47,175 --> 00:09:49,219
Wali Kota melihatnya saat lewat.

87
00:09:49,302 --> 00:09:50,220
Habislah kau.

88
00:09:50,303 --> 00:09:51,763
- Aku pergi.
- Cepatlah.

89
00:10:12,492 --> 00:10:14,494
Kau sudah mengambil cuti?

90
00:10:15,078 --> 00:10:16,538
Kau bilang

91
00:10:16,621 --> 00:10:19,582
tidak ada yang akan berkonsultasi
untuk sementara.

92
00:10:19,666 --> 00:10:21,835
Tetap saja. Ini terlalu cepat.

93
00:10:24,129 --> 00:10:26,422
Aku enggan minta bantuanmu kalau bisa,

94
00:10:26,506 --> 00:10:28,174
tapi aku terpaksa.

95
00:10:28,258 --> 00:10:29,258
Astaga.

96
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:31,511
Kau tak bisa cuti sekarang.

97
00:10:31,594 --> 00:10:33,555
Selamat berdiskusi.

98
00:10:38,518 --> 00:10:40,895
Ada orang gila menabrak median

99
00:10:40,979 --> 00:10:44,107
dan merusak pot gantung sejauh 50 meter.

100
00:10:44,691 --> 00:10:46,025
Aku harus apa?

101
00:10:47,068 --> 00:10:48,486
Jangan lakukan apa pun.

102
00:10:48,570 --> 00:10:50,280
Akan ditanggung asuransi.

103
00:10:50,363 --> 00:10:52,115
Kami bekerja keras memasangnya.

104
00:10:52,198 --> 00:10:54,826
Bukan hanya aku, tapi juga para lansia.

105
00:10:55,451 --> 00:10:59,122
Kami bekerja sambil didamprat pengemudi
karena menutup jalan.

106
00:11:00,832 --> 00:11:01,958
Aku akan bertindak.

107
00:11:02,041 --> 00:11:05,211
Akan kutuntut orang itu.
Aku yakin dia menyetir saat mabuk.

108
00:11:06,296 --> 00:11:07,672
Bukan mengemudi mabuk.

109
00:11:07,755 --> 00:11:09,465
Berarti mengemudi mengantuk.

110
00:11:09,549 --> 00:11:12,218
Orang yang tak mabuk
mustahil menabrak begitu.

111
00:11:13,052 --> 00:11:14,387
Remnya tak berfungsi.

112
00:11:15,471 --> 00:11:18,850
Kau memihak pelakunya sekarang?
Kau pengacara Balai Kota.

113
00:11:19,475 --> 00:11:22,061
Warga menuntut PNS karena hal sepele.

114
00:11:22,145 --> 00:11:23,605
Kami juga bisa menuntut.

115
00:11:23,688 --> 00:11:25,231
Dia penjahat.

116
00:11:25,315 --> 00:11:28,651
Menurut UU Perdata,
dia hanya menanggung kerugiannya.

117
00:11:28,735 --> 00:11:31,905
Dia membuat laporan,
staf perusahaan asuransi datang,

118
00:11:31,988 --> 00:11:33,531
polisi menyelidiki dia,

119
00:11:33,615 --> 00:11:35,783
dan dia buktikan itu tak disengaja.

120
00:11:35,867 --> 00:11:38,745
Jadi, dia tak melanggar
pasal KUHP, UU Lalin,

121
00:11:38,828 --> 00:11:40,371
atau Kecelakaan Lalin Khusus.

122
00:11:41,539 --> 00:11:44,209
Bagaimana kau tahu
itu disengaja atau tidak?

123
00:11:44,292 --> 00:11:47,045
Dia bilang itu tak disengaja?

124
00:11:48,796 --> 00:11:49,796
Ya.

125
00:11:51,216 --> 00:11:52,217
Kau bertemu dia?

126
00:11:53,927 --> 00:11:55,803
Kau bertemu dengannya sekarang.

127
00:11:58,097 --> 00:11:59,140
Apa…

128
00:12:01,309 --> 00:12:04,437
- Jangan bilang…
- Aku penyebab kecelakaan itu.

129
00:12:06,522 --> 00:12:08,775
Kenapa kau melakukan itu?

130
00:12:09,692 --> 00:12:11,861
Seharusnya tanya keadaanku, 'kan?

131
00:12:11,945 --> 00:12:14,364
Kau mencemaskan potnya, bukan aku?

132
00:12:14,447 --> 00:12:17,742
Kau tak apa-apa. Kau hadir
di rapat rencana pengembangan.

133
00:12:18,409 --> 00:12:20,286
Bagaimana kau tahu aku di sana?

134
00:12:24,374 --> 00:12:25,708
Kau tak membantu.

135
00:12:26,292 --> 00:12:27,794
Turunlah dan ajukan cuti.

136
00:12:28,628 --> 00:12:31,464
- Kutunggu di parkiran sepuluh menit lagi.
- Kenapa?

137
00:12:32,048 --> 00:12:33,591
Kita akan bepergian.

138
00:12:35,134 --> 00:12:37,720
- Untuk apa?
- Kau menjanjikan satu mantra

139
00:12:37,804 --> 00:12:39,931
dan sisanya untukmu sendiri.

140
00:12:40,014 --> 00:12:41,140
Berikan hari ini.

141
00:12:41,224 --> 00:12:43,184
Ini konyol.

142
00:12:43,268 --> 00:12:46,187
Kau menyuruhku cuti setelah merusak potku?

143
00:12:47,063 --> 00:12:49,524
Dengar. Ini situasi darurat.

144
00:12:49,607 --> 00:12:52,277
Aku harus membereskan kekacauan
yang kau buat.

145
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,529
Apa hanya kau staf di divisimu?

146
00:12:55,029 --> 00:12:58,032
- Yang lain bisa membereskannya.
- Itu tugasku.

147
00:12:58,116 --> 00:12:59,200
Aku lihat hierarkinya.

148
00:12:59,284 --> 00:13:02,495
Tugas staf lain berakhir
dalam satu atau dua baris,

149
00:13:02,578 --> 00:13:04,914
tapi kau tujuh baris.

150
00:13:05,873 --> 00:13:07,834
Itu tak adil.

151
00:13:07,917 --> 00:13:12,046
Suruh seniormu yang berleha-leha
untuk membereskannya.

152
00:13:13,715 --> 00:13:15,925
Ayo menghilang sehari.

153
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:22,056
KAFE ONJU

154
00:13:27,353 --> 00:13:29,981
Ini pasti
bukan tahun keberuntungan Hong-jo.

155
00:13:30,398 --> 00:13:33,359
Dia ditolak dan pekerjaannya hancur
keesokan harinya.

156
00:13:33,443 --> 00:13:35,236
Dia merebut target kita.

157
00:13:35,903 --> 00:13:37,071
Rasakan.

158
00:13:39,073 --> 00:13:39,907
Astaga.

159
00:13:39,991 --> 00:13:42,076
Hong-jo, kau di sini.

160
00:13:42,994 --> 00:13:44,495
Kau ada waktu bersantai?

161
00:13:45,413 --> 00:13:46,414
Urus masalah itu.

162
00:13:49,459 --> 00:13:50,459
"Astaga."

163
00:13:51,753 --> 00:13:54,797
"Apa yang baru saja kukatakan

164
00:13:54,881 --> 00:13:57,759
terdengar seperti pengakuan cinta?"

165
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:00,803
"Ya, menurutku begitu."

166
00:14:01,387 --> 00:14:02,387
"Apa itu bukan?"

167
00:14:03,097 --> 00:14:05,475
Terdengar sangat menyedihkan, 'kan?

168
00:14:08,478 --> 00:14:09,478
Astaga.

169
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:17,153
Pak Gong,

170
00:14:17,236 --> 00:14:18,654
- boleh aku…
- Apa? Cuti?

171
00:14:19,906 --> 00:14:22,992
- Ambillah.
- Apa?

172
00:14:24,494 --> 00:14:27,163
Aku tak memikirkannya kemarin.

173
00:14:27,747 --> 00:14:31,292
Sebaiknya ambil cuti
untuk mengobati patah hati.

174
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:38,758
<i>Ponsel dimatikan.
Tinggalkan pesan setelah nada berikut.</i>

175
00:14:38,841 --> 00:14:42,053
MA EUN-YEONG

176
00:14:42,136 --> 00:14:44,138
SEMUA BAIK-BAIK SAJA?

177
00:14:44,222 --> 00:14:45,973
EUN-YEONG, KAU TAK APA-APA?

178
00:14:48,226 --> 00:14:51,646
<i>Kau boleh balas dengan titik.</i>

179
00:15:03,282 --> 00:15:05,451
Kenapa orang terpelajar

180
00:15:05,535 --> 00:15:07,120
memercayai takhayul?

181
00:15:07,703 --> 00:15:10,164
Dia juga tak akan membayarku lebih.

182
00:15:10,248 --> 00:15:12,083
Kenapa aku harus mengikuti ini?

183
00:15:13,126 --> 00:15:15,795
Karena, jika kau punya pacar,
itu berkat aku.

184
00:15:19,382 --> 00:15:21,592
Kau pasti percaya takhayul.

185
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:23,636
Berikan.

186
00:15:23,719 --> 00:15:26,389
Orang terpelajar sepertimu
pakai Mantra Cinta?

187
00:15:26,472 --> 00:15:27,472
Berikan.

188
00:15:27,515 --> 00:15:29,308
Ambillah kalau bisa.

189
00:15:31,185 --> 00:15:32,770
Kitik-kitik.

190
00:15:46,159 --> 00:15:47,201
Ya, dapat.

191
00:15:53,124 --> 00:15:54,917
Aku tak memakai Mantra Cinta.

192
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:58,087
Halamannya hilang.

193
00:16:00,465 --> 00:16:01,632
Bukan itu.

194
00:16:02,383 --> 00:16:05,011
Aku pakai mantra untuk kurus atau cantik.

195
00:16:05,094 --> 00:16:06,512
Daya ingatku tajam.

196
00:16:06,596 --> 00:16:07,930
Aku ingat semuanya.

197
00:16:08,556 --> 00:16:11,642
Haruskah kubacakan bukunya
dari awal sampai akhir?

198
00:16:16,063 --> 00:16:18,900
Baiklah. Aku pakai Mantra Cinta.
Puas sekarang?

199
00:16:18,983 --> 00:16:20,526
Kau sangat cepat.

200
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:21,861
Kapan kau gunakan?

201
00:16:21,944 --> 00:16:25,323
Kau bilang itu punyaku.
Aku bebas menggunakannya.

202
00:16:28,993 --> 00:16:32,205
Buku mantranya berharga,
jadi masukkan ke kotak kayu.

203
00:16:32,955 --> 00:16:33,998
Pasti.

204
00:17:01,359 --> 00:17:02,401
<i>Apa dia minum?</i>

205
00:17:02,944 --> 00:17:03,944
<i>Pasti diminum.</i>

206
00:17:04,362 --> 00:17:06,447
<i>Semoga dia meminumnya.</i>

207
00:17:07,490 --> 00:17:08,991
Kenapa harus hari ini?

208
00:17:10,952 --> 00:17:13,371
Kebetulan aku mau hari ini.

209
00:17:14,622 --> 00:17:17,542
Pot gantungnya hancur total,

210
00:17:17,625 --> 00:17:18,834
tapi mobilmu mulus.

211
00:17:19,585 --> 00:17:21,254
Mobil itu di bengkel.

212
00:17:21,337 --> 00:17:23,714
Jadi, mobilmu ada dua.

213
00:17:23,798 --> 00:17:25,424
Ayahmu memberimu segalanya.

214
00:17:25,508 --> 00:17:27,927
Kau mau apa lagi dengan mantranya?

215
00:17:30,555 --> 00:17:31,973
Aku perlu tahu juga.

216
00:17:32,056 --> 00:17:35,726
Mantra apa yang kau inginkan
hingga kita pergi sejauh ini?

217
00:17:35,810 --> 00:17:36,978
Tenang saja.

218
00:17:37,061 --> 00:17:39,272
Aku tak mengambil Mantra Kulit Cerah.

219
00:17:49,490 --> 00:17:50,490
Omong-omong,

220
00:17:51,158 --> 00:17:54,036
apa ada yang terluka?

221
00:17:54,704 --> 00:17:56,789
Bagaimanapun, itu kecelakaan mobil.

222
00:17:57,456 --> 00:17:59,292
Kau mampu menyetir?

223
00:17:59,875 --> 00:18:01,502
Apa kau saja yang menyetir?

224
00:18:02,003 --> 00:18:02,837
Kau bisa?

225
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:04,922
Tentu saja bisa. Astaga!

226
00:18:05,006 --> 00:18:08,884
SIM-ku tersimpan di lemari,
jadi sangat mulus. Seharusnya kubawa.

227
00:18:08,968 --> 00:18:11,554
Kenapa SIM disimpan di lemari?
Akan kau pakai?

228
00:18:15,808 --> 00:18:17,310
Ini mobil kemudi otomatis.

229
00:18:17,393 --> 00:18:18,644
Tenang dan tidurlah.

230
00:18:19,895 --> 00:18:22,023
Aku bukan tipe yang tidur di mobil.

231
00:18:22,690 --> 00:18:24,775
Itu tak menghargai pengemudinya.

232
00:18:27,153 --> 00:18:29,155
Begitu rupanya.

233
00:18:36,078 --> 00:18:37,622
Mau berhenti di tempat…

234
00:18:39,790 --> 00:18:40,791
Kurasa tidak.

235
00:20:00,955 --> 00:20:04,208
<i>Wajahku memerah
hanya di depan orang yang kusukai.</i>

236
00:20:05,584 --> 00:20:09,922
<i>Apa yang baru saja kukatakan
terdengar seperti pengakuan cinta?</i>

237
00:20:27,773 --> 00:20:29,817
Son Sae-byeol dari Divisi RTH.

238
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:31,902
Apa Bu Lee sedang keluar?

239
00:20:33,195 --> 00:20:35,865
Apa kau Pak Kwon?

240
00:20:37,742 --> 00:20:38,826
