01:06:39,918 --> 01:06:41,002
Jadi, ada masalah.

722
01:06:42,545 --> 01:06:44,506
Tidak. Kami sangat cocok.

723
01:06:47,300 --> 01:06:49,761
Mustahil Mantra Cinta-nya ampuh.

724
01:06:50,887 --> 01:06:52,013
Kenapa seyakin itu?

725
01:06:52,096 --> 01:06:54,224
- Kau pikir aku ditolak?
- Tidak.

726
01:06:55,808 --> 01:06:57,977
Jae-gyeong memang menyukaimu.

727
01:07:01,147 --> 01:07:02,148
Lalu, aku

728
01:07:02,565 --> 01:07:03,983
juga menyukaimu.

729
01:07:54,659 --> 01:07:57,495
DESTINED WITH YOU

730
01:07:57,579 --> 01:07:59,998
Menyukaiku?

731
01:08:00,582 --> 01:08:01,958
<i>Kau pikir aku mau?</i>

732
01:08:02,041 --> 01:08:04,752
<i>Perasaanku tak terkendali
karena mantra itu.</i>

733
01:08:05,253 --> 01:08:06,462
Hentikan, Jang Sin-yu.

734
01:08:06,546 --> 01:08:07,839
<i>Kau mengikutiku?</i>

735
01:08:07,922 --> 01:08:08,922
Tidak.

736
01:08:09,299 --> 01:08:11,259
Ya. Sebenarnya, aku mengikutimu.

737
01:08:11,342 --> 01:08:14,345
<i>Aku tak mau ini.
Namun, tubuhku tak terkendali.</i>

738
01:08:14,429 --> 01:08:16,556
<i>Ajari aku cara mematahkan mantranya.</i>

739
01:08:16,639 --> 01:08:18,433
<i>Hanya ada satu cara.</i>

740
01:08:19,058 --> 01:08:20,226
Apa itu?

741
01:08:20,310 --> 01:08:22,145
<i>Bagaimana jika pada akhirnya aku</i>

742
01:08:22,729 --> 01:08:24,188
<i>sungguh mencintainya?</i>

